1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,800
Plastic doesn’t disappear; it just breaks down.

2
00:00:02,800 --> 00:00:07,600
Microplastics are tiny plastic fragments invading our oceans, lurking in every corner.

3
00:00:07,600 --> 00:00:13,600
They travel up the food web, from plankton to fish… and even into our plates.

4
00:00:13,600 --> 00:00:18,000
Research from NOAA shows microplastics can disrupt marine life and ecosystems.

5
00:00:18,000 --> 00:00:19,200
But don’t panic!

6
00:00:19,200 --> 00:00:22,800
Scientists are working to understand and tackle this issue.

7
00:00:22,800 --> 00:00:25,200
Stay informed and protect our oceans.

8
00:00:25,200 --> 00:00:28,400
Hit like and follow for more science insights!
